      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "This meticulously maintained vehicle represents a premier opportunity for the discerning driver. Demonstrating consistent mechanical integrity and a well-preserved interior, it has undergone a rigorous professional inspection to ensure peak operational performance. Offering a sophisticated balance of durability and modern comfort, this unit is prepared for immediate service. We invite you to experience the assurance of a vehicle curated for those who demand reliability and executive presence without compromise.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
